{"tid":1441183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我有個大膽的想法：將機場交畀左㬵起大台","createTime":"2019-08-10T15:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T03:49:48.000Z","uid":20867,"like":20,"dislike":193,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"40a14178fd3a15d8700cb299c7f750f0a6b67276","tid":1441183,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:11:29.000Z","msg":"1. 屬性<br />\n活動名叫「和你飛」說明 香港國際機場 的「和理非」屬性：<br />\n<br />\n系統<br />\n制度<br />\n秩序<br />\n安檢<br />\n<br />\n完全跟 抗爭者 格格不入。<br />\n<br />\n2. 地理<br />\n香港國際機場 遠離社區<br />\n雖然不利抗爭者<br />\n但卻能發揮左膠左 物資 和 物流 的優勢。<br />\n<br />\n3. 大台<br />\n2014金鐘大台 形成半封閉的社區<br />\n一潭死水 / 塘水滾塘魚 致民氣消散<br />\n<br />\n2019機場大台<br />\n是香港人面向國際的舞台<br />\n內鬼或對家 冇咁易耍陰招<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/02_p93LD_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F02_p93LD_1200x0.jpg&h=91d86b85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/04_29VEh_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F04_29VEh_1200x0.jpg&h=c959a6bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/07_RPrHz_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F07_RPrHz_1200x0.jpg&h=7e06176c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/03_qrJBp_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F03_qrJBp_1200x0.jpg&h=fde113fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n和理非的「和你飛」<br />\n蕭家怡2019/8/10 &mdash; 20:08<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%92%8C%E7%90%86%E9%9D%9E%E7%9A%84-%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0%E9%A3%9B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2592%258C%25E7%2590%2586%25E9%259D%259E%25E7%259A%2584-%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E9%25A3%259B%2F&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMs%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=835bca0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2592%258C%25E7%2590%2586%25E9%259D%259E%25E7%259A%2584-%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E9%25A3%259B%2F&h=c2d70c79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%92%8C%E7%90%86%E9%9D%9E%E7%9A%84-%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0%E9%A3%9B/</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 民意<br />\n如果香港人寧願放棄自己社區<br />\n都要走入和理非 機場大台<br />\n甚至聚到過萬人靜坐集會<br />\n亦系體現民主<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db01a11f6afbef0b7c142413172d0e89f8596c43","tid":1441183,"uid":30302,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:12:19.000Z","msg":"冇大台"},{"pid":"ed48e8d58f054eea1ea5eddb63c656622f167b53","tid":1441183,"uid":44698,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:13:01.000Z","msg":"胶你老未咩<br />\n死撚返支那喇3毛"},{"pid":"149bc0802e4fccacba619ddf968a4f1844b3ce55","tid":1441183,"uid":44929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:13:30.000Z","msg":"大你老母"},{"pid":"f0e0f80b632fd92a113997de411f30c4be9c56a9","tid":1441183,"uid":285854,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:13:56.000Z","msg":"大家善用不推文回覆"},{"pid":"72fd8b054eccc44f0a8eb06eb1b2a3bcbdc80161","tid":1441183,"uid":210682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:14:10.000Z","msg":"胶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=